flowchart TB
    %% Styling
    classDef npm fill:#cb3837,stroke:#fff,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef cli fill:#1e1b4b,stroke:#a855f7,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef commands fill:#1e3a8a,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef api fill:#14532d,stroke:#22c55e,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef env fill:#4c1d95,stroke:#8b5cf6,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Distribution
    subgraph Distribution [📦 Package Distribution]
         direction LR
         NPMRegistry[npmjs.com/package/careervivid]
         NPMInstall[npm install -g careervivid]
         NPMRegistry -.->|Global Install| NPMInstall
    end

    %% Internal CLI Structure
    subgraph Core [💻 CareerVivid CLI Core Program]
        direction TB
        Commander[Command Parser - Commander.js]
        ConfigStore[Local Config Store ~/.careervivid]
        OutputFormatter[Rich Terminal UI - Ora & Chalk]
        
        Commander <--> ConfigStore
        Commander --> OutputFormatter
    end

    %% Sub-commands
    subgraph Commands [⚡ Available Commands]
        direction LR
        cmdAuth[cv auth]
        cmdPublish[cv publish]
        cmdPortfolio[cv portfolio]
        cmdConfig[cv config]
    end

    %% User Environment
    subgraph UserEnv [🖥️ Developer Workspace]
        direction TB
        Terminal[Secure Terminal Session]
        MarkdownFiles[Local Markdown Articles .md]
        MermaidFiles[Local Mermaid Diagrams .mmd]
    end

    %% Backend APIs
    subgraph BackendAPIs [🌐 CareerVivid Core APIs]
        direction TB
        ApiAuth[SSO Authentication API]
        ApiPublish[Community Publish API]
        ApiPortfolio[Portfolio Management API]
    end

    %% Flow logic
    NPMInstall ==>|Executes| Terminal
    
    Terminal -->|Runs 'cv'| Commander
    Terminal -->|Authors| MarkdownFiles
    Terminal -->|Designs| MermaidFiles
    
    MarkdownFiles -.->|File Input| cmdPublish
    MermaidFiles -.->|File Input| cmdPublish
    
    Commander --> Commands
    
    cmdAuth ===|Browser OAuth| ApiAuth
    cmdPublish ===|Validated Payload| ApiPublish
    cmdPortfolio ===|Sync Projects/Assets| ApiPortfolio

    %% Applying styles
    class Distribution npm
    class Core cli
    class Commands commands
    class BackendAPIs api
    class UserEnv env
